
Overview of noun glaze

The noun glaze has 3 senses (no senses from tagged texts)
                                        
1. glaze -- (any of various thin shiny (savory or sweet) coatings applied to foods)
2. glaze -- (a glossy finish on a fabric)
3. glaze -- (a coating for ceramics, metal, etc.)

